'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 65''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 65''',  was the sixty-fifth issue of ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', released on [[August 17]], [[2006]] and covering [[September]] and [[October]] 2006. It was promoted as a "Lords of the Sith Collectors' Special Issue," and contained 100 pages.

